    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a great project car or a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small dents on the door panels, and some fading on the roof's clear coat. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and a small tear on the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that reflects its years on the road.",
